references:
  - type: article
    title: "Geometry First: Quantum Mechanics, Gravity, and the Origin of the Standard Model from a Single Conservation Law"
    authors:
      - family-names: Menendez
        given-names: Jack
    doi: 10.5281/zenodo.20078529
    year: 2026
    notes: "Paper I of the A=1 Discrete Causal Lattice series.  Original (continuous-amplitude) implementation of the framework that dcl_core re-implements with integer-token probability accounting; downstream papers in the series will pin specific Zenodo-deposited versions of dcl_core."
  - type: article
    title: "Geometry Forces Physics: A Lie-Algebra Derivation of the Standard Model Gauge Group from a Single Conservation Law"
    authors:
      - family-names: Menendez
        given-names: Jack
    doi: 10.5281/zenodo.20292158
    year: 2026
    notes: "Paper II of the A=1 Discrete Causal Lattice series.  Establishes the 71-dimensional per-site automorphism algebra and identifies 20 generators with Standard-Model degrees of freedom; the remaining 51 are the open structure that motivates the complex-carry hypothesis for dcl_core's BresenhamResidual (see notes/bresenham_residual_design.md)."
